Nodemcu.
5.Objectives
1.	Design a reliable emergency communication system for remote areas without cellular networks
2.	Implement LoRa-based hardware for long-range wireless transmission
3.	Develop a web dashboard for real-time emergency monitoring
4.	Integrate Google Maps API for victim location tracking
5.	Automate help center discovery using Google Places API
6. Future Enhancements
1.	Satellite Integration: Add Iridium or Starlink for global coverage
2.	AI-Powered Triage: Machine learning for emergency severity assessment
3.	Drone Integration: Autonomous drones for first aid delivery
4.	IoT Sensors: Environmental sensors (temperature, air quality)
5.	Blockchain: Secure, tamper-proof emergency records
6.	Mobile App: Dedicated mobile applications for better UX
7.	Multi-language Support: Localization for different regions
8.	Weather Integration: Real-time weather data for rescue planning
9.	Biometric Monitoring: Health vitals transmission (heart rate, etc.)
10.	Blockchain Verification: Immutable emergency record keeping
